⭐ One Important Suggestion
From tomorrow, I'd like you to do one extra thing. Whenever we write code, read it aloud in English.

For example: const Greeting = () => {}
Read it like this: Create a constant called Greeting. It stores a function.

Then return () Read: Return this JSX to React.

Then <h1>Hello</h1> Read: Display a heading saying Hello.
This habit may feel strange at first, but it will train you to understand code instead of memorizing it.

